description:
In the year 2026, a major nuclear conflict breaks out between nuclear superpowers, during which
the territory of the state of Phobos was devastated by a nuclear bomb. It&apos;s a terrible time. The country began to experience great losses: people began to die off and cities were emptied.
Nice days after the explosion, the surviving people noticed that the dead were &#x201C;alive&#x201D; in the devastated zone. The revived undead were aggressive to any form of life.
You have to forget what a calm life once was. Only those who can keep their spirits up will survive in this hell.

Features:
Arsenal of weapons (from a pistol, to a sniper rifle);
A huge open world;
Vehicles;
There is the possibility of crafting, building a shelter;
You must get yourself food, and watch your health;
Multiplayer mode
